---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Maryland Family Network Case Study | Upfront" description="See how Maryland Family Network partnered with Upfront to create a simple and intuitive way for families to find childcare.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-teal hover:text-brand-teal/80 transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to Case Studies
      </a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 mb-8">
        <img
          src="/images/partners/maryland-family-network.png"
          alt="Maryland Family Network logo"
          class="h-16 w-auto"
        />
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
        Maryland Family Network
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-gray">
        A Simple and Intuitive Way to Find Childcare
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-orange uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The Challenge
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        The Problem
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        Maryland Family Network (MFN) provides resources for families to ensure their child's first five years are successful through the Division of Early Childhood.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-6">
        LOCATE, its existing childcare search platform, had a few challenges:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">The family search site wasn't mobile-optimized, lacked provider pages, and had limited filters</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Childcare desert visualizations were based on data as old as a year prior</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-orange mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-brand-gray">Manually gathering data on family searches and provider gaps took hours every month</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Solution -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
        The Solution
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">
        A New LOCATE Portal
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray mb-8">
        Upfront and MFN collaborated to create a new LOCATE portal centered around ease of access, accurate information, and streamlined data.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Simple User Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            A seamless, mobile-friendly design. New filters for subsidy eligibility, special needs, and pricing.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 4m0 13V4m0 0L9 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Accurate Childcare Desert Maps</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            The first real-time gap visualizations in the country.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Automated Reports</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">
            Extensive, automated reports and dashboards showing family search behaviors, provider supply summaries.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Results -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-sm font-semibold text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
          The Results
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">
          Dramatic Improvements in ECE Data Access
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Upfront's new system quickly and dramatically improves ECE data access to families, providers, and advocates.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">2.5x</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            more families found childcare with the new LOCATE portal
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-teal mb-4">6,400</div>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-navy font-medium">
            individual provider pages created, creating a digital presence for 60% of Maryland's childcare programs
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-8">
          <img
            src="/images/testimonials/laura-weeldreyer.jpeg"
            alt="Laura Weeldreyer"
            class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover flex-shrink-0"
          />
          <div>
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-teal/20 mb-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z" />
            </svg>
            <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-navy font-medium mb-6">
              Technology should make lives easier - and that's exactly what Upfront does for Maryland families.
            </blockquote>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-brand-navy">Laura Weeldreyer</p>
              <p class="text-brand-gray">Executive Director, Maryland Family Network</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABanner />
</Layout>
